{"tid":437043,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"倘泛民自決派不協調　建制得利","createTime":"2017-10-15T15:34:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-16T03:01:01.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"97e5a5d7a2a66b5064f7cf3a965db6e31f7ed7f2","tid":437043,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T15:34:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20171015/20183500\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20171015%2F20183500&d=8rPCp%2BJ5%2FXENzZ2nkgJxcpWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=d963af66\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20171015%2F20183500&h=74f77b25\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20171015/20183500</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n倘泛民自決派不協調　建制得利<br />\n<br />\n6,657<br />\n ■青政有意派人參與九西補選，民協馮檢基亦早表態參選。<br />\n適中字型<br />\n較大字型<br />\n■青政有意派人參與九西補選，民協馮檢基亦早表態參選。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n【本報訊】青年新政有意派人參與立法會九龍西補選、再加上民協馮檢基早已表態參選，令非建制陣營出現多過一名候選人機會增加。<br />\n<br />\n不過，民主派在今屆立法會選舉中，合共15張名單競逐九龍西6個議席，雖然非建制最終取得4個議席，但按今屆立會選舉，各陣營在九西得票率分析，建制派得票率達37%，而民主、自決派各自得票率均不足三成，一旦非建制陣營出現多名候選人，失去補議席風險很高。<br />\n<br />\n根據2016區議會選舉的數據，民建聯蔣麗芸得票超過52,541票，經民聯梁美芬得49,745票，二人為建制派共奪約10萬票；非建制派的劉小麗有38,183票；公民黨毛孟靜以32,323票；民主黨黃碧雲26,037票；及游蕙禎以20,643票取得，非建制派合共取得不足12萬票。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2016建制得票稱冠九西<br />\n<br />\n以得票率分折，將同一陣營落選候選人的得票亦納入計算，建制派得票率為37%；傳統泛民主派得票率約29%；自決派得票率約28.3%，若傳統泛民及自決派各自支持不同候選人出戰，而建制陣營只出一人，非建制派要取回九西議席有相當風險。<br />\n<br />\n■記者陳嘉裕  <br />\n<br />\n[img]<a href=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20171015/large/a0802a.gif\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171015%2Flarge%2Fa0802a.gif&d=8rPCp%2BJ5%2FXENzZ2nkgJxcpWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=51f8ade3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171015%2Flarge%2Fa0802a.gif&h=4310c0eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20171015/large/a0802a.gif</a><br />\n[/img]<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n九西補選劉小麗讓路青政　盼民主派凝聚共識重奪議席<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n伍凱欣︰羅雅寧不參選令選票更集中"},{"pid":"35910d3301d7e0171b465903946f8a84e262a538","tid":437043,"uid":47359,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T15:36:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">食屎啦LIKLN<br />\n聯合五毛投訴濕鳩塞鷗搞到佢俾人bam<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"e53c92cf357838c7b9aa9e8502db62734aceef9e","tid":437043,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T15:49:37.000Z","msg":"政治篩選入閘+修改議事規則(無得搵布+限制發音時間及次數)<br />\n<br />\n想問選出來仲有咩用？"},{"pid":"f4c193ef3053ee88eeb4fc40c0b679176fb4cf0a","tid":437043,"uid":20816,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T15:55:23.000Z","msg":"樓主心理變態"},{"pid":"49954063cb486f0cfa25dd4dd4682003b6cc0247","tid":437043,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T15:56:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>政治篩選入閘+修改議事規則(無得搵布+限制發音時間及次數)<br />\n<br />\n想問選出來仲有咩用？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇用仲爭，已經搞成咁仲鬥，樣樣都冇用，上街又不了"},{"pid":"a8c9a05fd6a0d4ce04d0df1399724f522df24e79","tid":437043,"uid":21028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T15:59:11.000Z","msg":"六年前講過 個個想做大佬 根本佢地利字當頭"},{"pid":"c4c452f604626d3f2bca062d9af0925229a8da0e","tid":437043,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T16:05:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>六年前講過 個個想做大佬 根本佢地利字當頭</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好失望，見成班內鬥到支離破碎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但我仍希望大家醒悟，搞初選出一個啦，笨7"},{"pid":"9db1674a3c4bfd8b8ea8070553ec75b87f4dca66","tid":437043,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T02:34:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: